  "prompt": "What's your definition of \"friends\"?",
  "response": "\"Friends\" can be defined as individuals who share a mutual bond of affection, trust, and support. They often engage in social activities together, communicate openly, and provide emotional or practical assistance during both good times and bad. Friendships can vary in closeness and duration, ranging from casual acquaintances to deep, long-lasting connections. The essence of friendship typically includes respect, understanding, and an enjoyable companionship.",
